nodes.text: Star Wars Rebels: Storybook Library is a compilation box-set featuring eight previously published Star Wars Rebels young readers titles. The titles featured are Chopper Saves the Day, Property of Ezra Bridger, Ezra's Wookiee Rescue, Art Attack, The Inquisitor's Trap, TIE Fighter Trouble, Entanglement and Who Are the Rebels? The box set features a 3/4 slip case and also includes an 18 x 18 poster and two 9 x 9 sticker sheets.

Though announced for a release date of December 22, 2014, with provided cover art, the title did not appear in listings on retailers such as Amazon and Barnes & Noble. It was eventually released through retailers including Amazon at a later date.
